rows.label: qev095404_MSG0001
rows.name:
All my men could not kill indigen. But you did.
You made it look easy.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev095404_MSG0004
rows.name: Run! All of you! I will protect injured.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev095404_SEL0011
rows.name: Offer to bring these Prone to New LA as captives.

rows.label: qev095404_MSG0007
rows.name: Enough, Captain. We must do as [ST:gender p1=he p2=she ] says.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev095404_MSG0008
rows.name: Our lives are in [ST:gender p1=his p2=her ] hands.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev095404_MSG0011
rows.name: I do not trust Earth aliens.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev095404_MSG0012
rows.name: But if there is chance you save my men, I must take it.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev095404_MSG0014
rows.name: Go on, Earth alien. Do as you will.[ST:wait ]
